<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .login-container {
          background-color: #f2f2f2;
          padding: 70px;
          width: 300px;
          text-align: center;
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
        }

        .login-container h1 {
          font-size: 18px;
          margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .welcome {
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        .login-container input {
          display: block;
          width: 90%;
          padding: 18px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          border: none;
          background-color: #d9d9d9;
        }

        .login-container button {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 18px;
          background-color: #FF894E;
          border: none;
          font-weight: bold;
          cursor: pointer;
        }

        .login-container label {
          font-size: 12px;
          display: block;
          margin: 10px 0 5px;
          text-align: left;
          padding-left: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="login-container">
    <h1>냉장고를 부탁해</h1>
    <div class="welcome">환영합니다!</div>
    <form action="/refri/join" method="post">
        <label for="email">새 이메일</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

        <label for="password">새 비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required> <br>

        <button type="submit">가입하기</button>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
